    "processing.toGridItems": {
      "id": "processing.toGridItems",
      "version": "1.1.0",
      "kind": "processing",
      "title": "Canvas assignments ‚Üí GridItem[] (batched; returns url; no status in output)",
      "deps": [
        "data.assignmentsRaw@^1.0.0"
      ],
      "contracts": {
        "touch": [
          {
            "$ref": "node:data.assignmentsRaw@^1.0.0#types.CanvasAssignmentRaw"
          }
        ],
        "produces": {
          "GridItem": {
            "id": "string",
            "title": "string",
            "dueAt?": "iso8601",
            "points?": "int",
            "url": "string",
            "attentionType": "enum[Check|Thumb|Question|Warning|Hand]"
          }
        }
      },
      "signature": {
        "input": {
          "entries[]": {
            "assignment": {
              "$ref": "node:data.assignmentsRaw@^1.0.0#types.CanvasAssignmentRaw"
            },
            "checkpointStatus": "enum[Due|Missing|Submitted|Graded]"
          },
          "formatType": "enum[Prior|Weekday|Next]",
          "asOf": "iso8601",
          "timezone?": "IANA_tz"
        },
        "output[]": {
          "$ref": "#contracts.produces.GridItem"
        }
      },
      "processing": {
        "pipeline": [
          {
            "id": "toGridItems",
            "kind": "pure",
            "rules": [
              "Precompute once per call (do not recompute per element):",
              "- Parse `asOf` into the specified `timezone` (IANA) using date-fns-tz; fallback to ISO offset if no tz provided.",
              "- Derive `asOfWeekday` (0‚Äì6, Sun..Sat).",
              "- Compute `prevFridayInstant(asOf,tz)` and `prevDayInstant(asOf,tz)`.",
              "- Prepare formatters: `fmtMd` ‚Üí 'M/d', `fmtEEE` ‚Üí 'EEE'.",
              "For each entry in `entries` (preserve input order):",
              "- Map `id` ‚Üê assignment.id (required, non-empty).",
              "- Map `points` ‚Üê clamp(assignment.points_possible, min=0); omit if null/undefined *except* title always shows a number (use 0 when points missing).",
              "- Map `dueAt` ‚Üê assignment.due_at if valid ISO8601 *with timezone*; otherwise omit.",
              "- Map `url` ‚Üê assignment.html_url || assignment.url || compose from known ids; must start with http(s).",
              "- Build `name` ‚Üê trim and collapse internal whitespace from assignment.name.",
              "- Build `title` (depends on `formatType`; if `dueAt` missing, omit any date prefix):",
              "  ‚Ä¢ Prior:   `${fmtMd(dueAt)}: ${name} (${pointsOrZero})`",
              "  ‚Ä¢ Weekday: `${name} (${pointsOrZero})`",
              "  ‚Ä¢ Next:    `${fmtEEE(dueAt)}: ${name} (${pointsOrZero})`",
              "- Derive `attentionType` from `(checkpointStatus, dueAt, asOf)`:",
              "  ‚Ä¢ If checkpointStatus ‚àà {Submitted, Graded} ‚Üí 'Check'.",
              "  ‚Ä¢ Else if checkpointStatus = 'Due' ‚Üí 'Thumb'.",
              "  ‚Ä¢ Else (checkpointStatus = 'Missing'):",
              "      ‚Äì If asOf weekday ‚àà {Sat,Sun,Mon} AND dueAt == previous Friday (same tz) ‚Üí 'Question'.",
              "      ‚Äì Else if asOf weekday ‚àà {Tue,Wed,Thu,Fri} AND dueAt == (asOf - 1 day) (same tz) ‚Üí 'Question'.",
              "      ‚Äì Else ‚Üí 'Warning'.",
              "Determinism requirements:",
              "- `fmtEEE(dueAt)` must match the actual weekday of `dueAt` in the chosen timezone (add test).",
              "- No global mutable state; memoize helpers inside the call.",
              "Validation per element (fail fast for that element, continue others):",
              "- `id` non-empty; `url` begins with http(s); if `dueAt` exists, it must be ISO8601-with-tz."
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
